snippet.title: Luminous Trailer
snippet.description:
Luminous, a dark pixel-art platformer. Guide Keith through a darkened wasteland on a quest to rekindle the light. Can you bear the weight of your destiny?

This game is definitely not a metaphor for anything. No way.

Get Luminous now at https://jellyfish-ink.itch.io/luminous.

Music by Liam Holloway-Bidwell.
Pixel Operator Font by Jayvee Enaguas, used under the STL Open Font License (https://opensource.org/licenses/OFL-1.1).
